contentrichtext.text: '''Young Man with a Horn''' may refer to: * [[Young Man with a Horn (novel)|''Young Man with a Horn'' (novel)]], a novel by Dorothy Baker, loosely based on the life of Bix Beiderbecke * [[Young Man with a Horn (film)|''Young Man with a Horn'' (film)]], a film adaptation of the novel * [[Young Man with a Horn (soundtrack)|''Young Man with a Horn'' (soundtrack)]], an album featuring Doris Day and Harry James performing songs from the film's soundtrack * [[Young Man With A Horn (Miles Davis album)|''Young Man With A Horn'' (Miles Davis album)]], a 10" jazz album on Blue Note by the Miles Davis Sextet * [[Young Man with a Horn (CSI episode)|"Young Man with a Horn" (''CSI'' episode)]], a ninth season episode of ''CSI: Crime Scene Investigation'' {{disambig}}
